title: KEEPING UP WITH KEEPING UP
description: Charlotte & Leanne are graced with the presence of Cari Bonilla and Marina Hyson - two of the masterminds behind the Kardashian course at Brown University. The ladies share their experiences from developing the course to appearing on Keeping Up With The Kardashians. This episode digs beyond social media and the TV show and into how the Kardashians have truly influenced culture today. An intellectual conversation about the Kardashian family? Yep, it exists.
dc:creator: Gimlet Gals
